v&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31993491&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=13825540896888889ac35b86_48610903"/><published>2025-07-29T10:58:55+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>04f7a2702b8481ebafdcb857b6495a6b</id><title>北水加速買地產股 持倉倍增總額181億元 佔自由流通股6.4%</title><updated>2025-07-29T11:30:05+08:00</updated><author><name>aq6aq6</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-29T11:30:05+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573400466"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573400466"&gt;「港股通」今年來淨流入金額已突破去年全年，達8200億創新高，北水除了愛掃入內銀、國企等傳統高息股外，今年亦加速掃入本地地產股。花旗早前發表報告，除認為本港樓市接近見底，又提及截至今年6月底，南下資金對11隻市值合計9450億元「港股通」地產股&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31993507&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=13825540896888889ac35b86_48610903"/><published>2025-07-29T11:30:05+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>af9aa1dbef72887d2d3cdec32848f38b</id><title>彭楚盈遇害地點 係咪同層都叫凶宅？</title><updated>2025-07-29T12:19:38+08:00</updated><author><name>我今天放假</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-29T12:19:38+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573401048"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573401048"&gt;睇完方東昇個節目好奇個單位樓價&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31993532&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=13825540896888889ac35b86_48610903"/><published>2025-07-29T12:19:38+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>83aa465a3ab17ac164fd18799de24e22</id><title>22年經驗A